J. Schmidhuber. Simple Algorithmic Theory of Subjective Beauty, Novelty, Surprise, Interestingness, Attention, Curiosity, Creativity, Art, Science, Music, Jokes. Journal of SICE, 48(1):21-32, 2009. PDF.

J. Schmidhuber. Art &amp; science as by-products of the search for novel patterns, or data compressible in unknown yet learnable ways. In M. Botta (ed.), Multiple ways to design research. Research cases that reshape the design discipline, Milano-Lugano, Swiss Design Network - Et al. Edizioni, 2009, pp. 98-112. PDF.

J. Schmidhuber. Artificial Scientists &amp; Artists Based on the Formal Theory of Creativity. In Proceedings of the Third Conference on Artificial General Intelligence (AGI-2010), Lugano, Switzerland. PDF.

